# Riverpod provider definitions per specs/shared/system-architecture.md "State scoping".
# Organized by scope:
#   app_providers.dart      - app scope (registries, platform adapters, settings)
#   device_providers.dart   - device scope (kid profile index, last-active kid)
#   kid_providers.dart      - kid scope (mastery, inventory, library, counters)
#   session_providers.dart  - session scope (activity runner, lesson runner, round state)
